# Next.js App Router

- **Layouts & pages**: Default to **Server Components**. Export `metadata` (and fonts) from `layout.tsx` using `next/font` where the site typography is set.
- **Dynamic routes**: When data is a static map keyed by URL segment, use `generateStaticParams()` that returns the same keys as the data (see `src/app/experience/[id]/page.tsx`).
- **Route Handlers** (`app/api/**/route.ts`): Use `NextRequest` / `NextResponse` from `next/server`. Do **not** use Pages Router types `NextApiRequest` / `NextApiResponse` in App Router files.
- **Styling entry**: Global styles are imported from `src/app` (e.g. `./globals.css` in the root layout).
